# Simple Text Editor with Undo (Stack-based)

## 🧠 Objective
A terminal-based text editor that supports:
- Adding characters
- Deleting the last character
- Undoing the last operation using a stack

## 📂 Project Structure
- `text_editor.py`: Core logic
- `test_text_editor.py`: Unit tests
- `flowchart.png`: Operation flowchart
- `clarifying_questions.md`: Clarifying assumptions
- `complexity_analysis.md`: Time and space analysis

## ▶️ How to Run
```bash
python3 text_editor.py
